I"r<h1 id="pontifications">Pontifications</h1>

<ul>
  <li>Avoid the word easy when it comes to features (or <a href="http://rolandtanglao.com/2019/11/28/p1-howto-remove-condesceding-language-from-documentation/">documentation</a>) &lt;— tl;dr from I<a href="https://inessential.com/2019/11/03/this_feature_should_be_easy">nessential: This Feature Should Be Easy</a></li>
  <li>Nothing is easy! Please continue to report bugs and ask for feature requests, just don’t use the words <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">easy</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">should</code>!</li>
</ul>

